  [info] Redundant rebinding
   ╭─[test.lis:4:3]
 3 │   let a = 5;
 4 │   let a = a;
   ·   ────┬────
   ·       ╰── rebinds `a` to itself
 5 │   let _ = a
   ╰────
  help: Remove `let a = a`. The existing `a` already refers to this value, so rebinding it does nothing · code: [lint.redundant_rebinding]
